unit" rel="wikipedia">Control Unit</a></li><li>2-&gt;1 <a class="zem_slink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multiplexer" title="Multiplexer" rel="wikipedia">Multiplexers</a></li><li>TriState Buffers</li></ul><span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: medium; ">Parts List:</span><span class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: medium; "><br /></span><ul style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: medium; "><li>3 Registers</li><li>1 ALU</li><li>1 Program Counter</li><li>1 <a class="zem_slink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Address_bus" title="Address bus" rel="wikipedia">Address</a> Latch</li></ul> 
